'''Yma Nalle''' was one of the [[Nalle triplets]], a trio of [[Human/Legends|Humans]] offered by [[Mayor/Legends|Mayor]] [[Acros-Krik]] as guides to targets he wanted monitored. She reported to the mayor any useful information their guests foolishly divulged.

She was in the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] before the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|outbreak]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].

==Behind the scenes==
Yma Nalle was portrayed by [[Amy Allen]] (uncredited) in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']]. The name is an anagram of "Amy Allen."

